'''Randall de Jager''' (4 Mata 1971 - 22 Ukuboza 2001), yari mukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika yepfo]] . Yamenyekanye cyane kubera uruhare rwe muri serial izwi cyane ''Egoli: Place of Gold'' na 7de Laan . <ref>https://www.all4women.co.za/689929/entertainment/celebrity-photo-galleries/gallery-soapie-stars-who-died-in-real-life/2</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 4 Mata 1971 mu nkengero za Bishop Lavis, Cape Town, [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]. Afite imyaka 17, yabaye umwarimu watozaga abandi ku cyumweru kandi yegeranye cyane nitorero. Yakuranye na nyina, Jean kandi afite bashiki be babiri: Juanita, Angelique na murumuna we Roger. <ref name="IOL">https://www.iol.co.za/travel/south-africa/hundreds-gather-for-funeral-of-7de-laan-star-79650</ref> Yakundanye kuva kera n'inshuti ye y'umukobwa, Kim Nichols.

== Urupfu ==
Mu ntangiriro za 22 Ukuboza 2001, Jager yakomerekejwe bikomeye n’ubujura bwitwaje imbunda mu nzu iri mu nkengero z'umujyi wa River Club, i Sandton, mu majyaruguru ya Johannesburg. Yapfiriye mu bitaro bya Johannesburg. Yari kumwe n'inshuti ye n'umukinnyi wa filime Helene Lombard mugihe cy'ubujura. Yarashwe mu maso hatangaza ko ubwonko bwangiritse cyane. <ref>https://www.news24.com/News24/Friend-tells-of-actors-death-20011224</ref> <ref>https://www.news24.com/News24/Actor-killed-in-robbery-20011222</ref>

umubirir we wimuriwe gushyingurwa i bishop Lavis i Cape Town . <ref name="IOL" /> Umuhango wo kwibuka wabereye mu rusengero rushya rw’Intumwa ku ya 29 Ukuboza. <ref>https://www.geni.com/people/Randall-de-Jager/6000000130132265852</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1992, yakinnye mu ikinamico ikinamico ''Paradise iri hafi'' . Mu 1998, yabaye umwanditsi, aho yanditse ikinamico ''Moenie Gerageza Nie'' . <ref>https://esat.sun.ac.za/index.php/Randall_de_Jager</ref> Azwiho uruhare rwa 'Hector' muri opera yisabune ya tereviziyo ''Egoli: Place of Gold''. Yakinnye kandi nk'umufasha wibitabo Aubrey Rudolph muri seri izwi cyane ya televiziyo ''7de Laan'' .

